sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controller Manager
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NGCAPI as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read InferenceService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService details
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create TriggerAuthentication<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: NIM Account Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Account CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Webhook validation request<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Read NGC API key Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Secret data
    Webhook->>NGCAPI: Validate NGC API key<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGCAPI-->>Webhook: Validation response
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: Account Ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Webhook Admission Control

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resource<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission webhook request<br/>Port: 443→9443/TCP<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation/Mutation response
    K8sAPI-->>User: Resource created/updated

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics endpoint<br/>Port: 8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
